[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'has created to help walk you through creating high-quality outputs just like this. It even works for digital apps. So, if you have a health app that you want to promote, for example, this health app, you can create this using'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the Hicksfield skill without even opening After Effects, Blender, Cinema 4D, any of those super heavy knowledge-based animation platforms. Everything can be done inside of your Claude session and the Hicksfield MCP.'

