[06:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'want to create it\'s going to prompt us through some questions. Which style do we want first classic motion or hyper and kinetic? I am going to go with just classic motion. I\'m going to have this only be 10 seconds long. It\'s going to be using Seed ants 2.0. There\'s a 15'

[06:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'second limit on the Seed ants outputs. So you can have a max of 15 seconds but for now I\'m just going to do a 10 second video. For our frame format I want to do 16 by 9 horizontal. And then do we have existing assets? No we don\'t so create'

[06:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'them for me. It\'s now going to ask us a second set of questions. What is the overall mood or aesthetic? I want it to feel more minimalist so a lot of negative space, restrained palette and a refined type. And then the storyboard'

